+## report vault
+
+Creates a beginning-to-end recovery report for the local vault.
+
+```text
+python pala.py report vault --all
+```
+
+Useful filters:
+
+| Option | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--all` | Include every record |
+| `--date 2026-06-09` | Limit to one date folder |
+| `--source codex` | Limit by source |
+| `--project trugurpala/pala-memory-core` | Limit by linked project |
+| `--tag mobile-share` | Require a tag |
+| `--output report.md` | Write to a custom Markdown path |
+| `--json` | Print machine-readable report metadata |
+
