+# v0.13 Vault Report
+
+Date: 2026-06-09
+Phase: vault recovery report preview
+Status: PASS for beginning-to-end vault report and scoped backup options
+
+## Goal
+
+Create one report that summarizes the local memory vault from beginning to end: records, sources, projects, tags, files, tasks, decisions, evidence, timeline, and backup artifacts.
+
+## Added Behavior
+
+| Area | Change |
+|---|---|
+| CLI | Added `python pala.py report vault` |
+| Scope | Supports `--all`, `--date`, `--source`, `--project`, and `--tag` |
+| Output | Writes Markdown under `data/reports/` by default |
+| JSON | Supports `python pala.py report vault --json` |
+| Backup | Added `--all` and `--date` to `backup receipt` |
+| Backup | Added `--all`, `--date`, `--source`, `--project`, and `--tag` to `backup github` and `backup drive` |
+
+## Commands
+
+```powershell
+python .\pala.py report vault --all
+python .\pala.py report vault --all --json
+python .\pala.py backup receipt --all
+python .\pala.py backup github --all --knowledge-bank .\data\backups\kb-vault-smoke
+python .\pala.py backup drive --all --target .\data\backups\drive-vault-smoke
+```
+
+## Smoke Test
+
+Executed in `C:\Users\Pala-Home-1\Desktop\Codex\pala-memory-core`:
+
+```powershell
+python -m py_compile .\pala.py
+python .\pala.py report vault --all
+python .\pala.py report vault --all --json | python -m json.tool
+python .\pala.py backup receipt --all
+python .\pala.py backup github --all --knowledge-bank .\data\backups\kb-vault-smoke
+python .\pala.py backup drive --all --target .\data\backups\drive-vault-smoke
+```
+
+Observed key output:
+
+```text
+vault report saved data\reports\2026-06-09-vault-all-report.md
+scope=all records=8 attachments=2 open_tasks=1
+receipt saved data\backups\2026-06-09-backup-receipt.md
+github backup package saved ...\pala-memory-core-all-backup
+records=8 artifacts=3 committed=False pushed=False
+drive backup package saved ...\pala-memory-core-all-drive-backup
+records=8 artifacts=3
+```
+
+Observed report sections:
+
+```text
+## Sources
+## Projects
+## Tags
+## Backup Status
+## Latest Backup Artifacts
+## Attachments
+## Open Tasks
+## Decisions
+## Evidence
+## Timeline
+```
+
+## Release Posture
+
+This is a recovery/report preview. It does not yet update each individual record's backup status after a backup package is pushed. It does provide a useful beginning-to-end Markdown report that can be backed up or shared.
